{"tid":1640410,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[迷思]到底中國市場對NBA嚟講有幾大","createTime":"2019-10-09T03:03:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T08:24:21.000Z","uid":28152,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5d1cf4a8cb8e523313a9973363532a3ee3e1af79","tid":1640410,"uid":28152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:03:59.000Z","msg":"中國邏輯就係郁啲都話自己有十四億人市場，騰訊話有4.9億個NBA觀眾，望落好似係一個好大嘅市場，但到底中國對NBA嚟講，係一塊幾大嘅餅呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先睇轉播費有幾多係嚟自中國:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2019/oct/08/adam-silver-nba-china-tv-broadcasts-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fsport%2F2019%2Foct%2F08%2Fadam-silver-nba-china-tv-broadcasts-hong-kong&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJ0YD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=67d5c477\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2019/oct/08/adam-silver-nba-china-tv-broadcasts-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\n根據衛報quote嘅數字，騰訊同nba有份五年1.5bn美金嘅轉播合約，由2020賽季開始<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/game/9zml2mj.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fgame%2F9zml2mj.html&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJ0YD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=0f49ec3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/game/9zml2mj.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2015年，NBA官方宣佈騰訊以5億美元（31.2億人民幣）獲得NBA未來五個賽季的網絡獨家直播權，該協議自2015年7月1日起生效。<br />\n<br />\n即係由2015賽季起計十年，中國轉播費有1.5bn+0.5bn=2bn=二十億美金收入，每年計返係200m<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_Basketball_Association_on_television\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FNational_Basketball_Association_on_television&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJ0YD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=dd6758c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_Basketball_Association_on_television</a><br />\n<br />\nOn October 6, 2014, NBA announced a nine-year $24 billion ($2.7 billion/year) extension with ESPN, ABC and Turner Sports beginning with the 2016&ndash;17 season and running through the 2024&ndash;25 season<br />\n<br />\n淨係睇呢單deal，九年有24bn美金，每年係有2.667bn<br />\n<br />\n計返% : 0.2 / ( 2.667+0.2) = 7%<br />\n<br />\n贊助費<br />\n<br />\n未搵到靚嘅數字，但可以從波衫同主場廣告攞下感覺。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sponsorship.com/Report/2018/05/14/Sponsorship-Spending-On-The-NBA-Totals-$1-12-Billi.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sponsorship.com%2FReport%2F2018%2F05%2F14%2FSponsorship-Spending-On-The-NBA-Totals-%241-12-Billi.aspx&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJ0YD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=8e1d7289\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sponsorship.com/Report/2018/05/14/Sponsorship-Spending-On-The-NBA-Totals-$1-12-Billi.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n另外根據呢個網，無一個大sponsor係中國公司。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0czaO13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0czaO13.jpg&h=4fcfbab3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n零售唔使講，有幾多係會買正版波衫波鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打有多啲料講多啲，等大家唔好誤為中國市場就等於好大好重要"},{"pid":"acb11f8a7fb15aee7f4b277da91bf51e680cee13","tid":1640410,"uid":28152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:11:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e671ac73305fc32239bdb7b69c84ef062f272c9","tid":1640410,"uid":109985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:14:47.000Z","msg":"同埋宜家單方面唔播都應該要賠錢？"},{"pid":"5af59c4340d615a9d2f744ddaf81f552548e96f4","tid":1640410,"uid":183090,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:18:21.000Z","msg":"你唔睇英超可以睇西甲, 但無第二個 league 可以取代NBA<br />\n況且本土嘅轉播權先係最賺錢, 呢班先係老細"},{"pid":"1b6614256b81fc4f9270bda7f1891486e2348562","tid":1640410,"uid":19552,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:20:44.000Z","msg":"香港人都比旅遊業騎劫啦 班撚樣講到旅遊業養起香港 原來GDP得4%關佢事"},{"pid":"119b2b9bf18cf7f9bc2ba52